---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-bone-400/10 bg-ink-900">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-wide gap-10 px-6 py-16 sm:grid-cols-2 sm:px-10 lg:grid-cols-4">
    <div class="lg:col-span-2">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="grid h-8 w-8 place-items-center rounded-full border border-mint/60 font-display text-sm font-semibold text-mint">PB</span>
        <span class="font-display text-sm tracking-tight text-bone-100">Philip Beadle</span>
      </div>
      <p class="body mt-6 max-w-narrow text-sm">
        Founder of AgenticScale.ai. Co-founding AgenticGrid Foundation. Seven years on the Holochain core team.
        AI-powered simulations that let every stakeholder in the energy transformation work together.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Companies</p>
      <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm">
        <li><a href="https://agenticscale.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-bone-200 hover:text-mint">AgenticScale.ai</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://ioen.tech" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-bone-200 hover:text-mint">IOEN.tech</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.racefor2030.com.au/project/agenticgrid-ai-breaking-the-barriers-with-ai-assisted-energy-modelling/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-bone-200 hover:text-mint">RACE project</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Network</p>
      <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm">
        <li><a href="https://www.holochain.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-bone-200 hover:text-mint">Holochain</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://holo.host" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-bone-200 hover:text-mint">Holo</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://unyt.co" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-bone-200 hover:text-mint">Unyt</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-bone-400/10">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-wide flex-col items-start justify-between gap-3 px-6 py-6 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest text-bone-400 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:px-10">
      <p>© {year} Philip Beadle · Melbourne, Australia</p>
      <p>Built with Astro. Designed for the long arc.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
